&lt;p&gt;Flagship Pioneering invents and builds platform companies, each with the potential for multiple products that transform human health, sustainability and beyond. Since its launch in 2000, Flagship has originated more than 100 companies. Many of these companies have addressed humanity’s most urgent challenges: vaccinating billions of people against COVID-19, curing intractable diseases, improving human health, preempting illness, and feeding the world by improving the resiliency and sustainability of agriculture.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flagship has been recognized twice on FORTUNE’s “Change the World” list, an annual ranking of companies that have made a positive social and environmental impact through activities that are part of their core business strategies and has been twice named to Fast Company’s annual list of the World’s Most Innovative Companies. Learn more about Flagship at&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://nam12.safelinks.protection.outlook.com/?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.flagshippioneering.com%2F&amp;amp;data=05%7C02%7Cemccurdy%40flagshippioneering.com%7C8e54295c994c4d440a7b08ddc94a4a72%7Cd00b8682fc8b4548b82dda0524788e9b%7C0%7C0%7C638888043086011906%7CUnknown%7CTWFpbGZsb3d8eyJFbXB0eU1hcGkiOnRydWUsIlYiOiIwLjAuMDAwMCIsIlAiOiJXaW4zMiIsIkFOIjoiTWFpbCIsIldUIjoyfQ%3D%3D%7C0%7C%7C%7C&amp;amp;sdata=gknIK%2BmYfQpsSi0%2FyQmhzNBo4DurYfmbUQpruIKf6Mc%3D&amp;amp;reserved=0&quot;&gt;www.flagshippioneering.com&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Flagship, we accept impossible missions to enable bigger leaps. Our&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.flagshippioneering.com/values&quot;&gt;core values&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;guide us through uncertainty and toward lasting impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;strong&gt;Accountant&lt;/strong&gt; will be responsible for ensuring the accuracy of financial reporting and providing strategic insights to support business decisions. This role requires a deep understanding of accounting principles, excellent analytical skills, and the ability to excel in a fast-paced, start-up environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform day-to-day accounting operations activities including expense reports/system administration, bill review, and cash and credit card reconciliations for multiple portfolio companies. Management of the AR function as applicable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform the month-end/quarter-end/year-end close activities timely and accurately, including posting and preparation of journal entries, external research and accrual tracking, and reconciliation of various balance sheet accounts for multiple portfolio companies in accordance with the monthly close calendar.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monthly update of forecast files with actuals and upload to NSPB, as well as troubleshooting/variance analysis of any discrepancies arising between the systems after the upload is complete.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage fixed assets and finance &amp;amp; operating leases, ensuring that policies and accounting guidance are followed.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Tracking of orders, delivery, and in-service dates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Monthly administrative tasks including payroll reconciliations, benefits reconciliations, new-hire support and documentation, and additional ad hoc requirements as they arise, such as 83(b) preparation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and support annual audits (as applicable), statutory filings, debt compliance reporting, investor reporting, and tax filings, ensuring all necessary documentation is prepared and available.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to provide financial insights and support business operations. This often includes but is not limited to: Labs teams/emp

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE ROLE&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At &lt;strong&gt;Flagship Pioneering&lt;/strong&gt;, we don’t wait for the future—we build it. Our origination model is like a startup foundry for breakthrough science and technology: we dream up bold ideas, pressure-test them fast, and launch entirely new ventures from scratch. Think of it as startup creation in extreme mode—where the whiteboard is blank, the questions are audacious, and the upside is industry-shaping.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated and innovative individual to join our interdisciplinary&amp;nbsp;team. As an &lt;strong&gt;Origination Associate&lt;/strong&gt;, you will contribute at the confluence of biomedical engineering, applied physics, devices and chemistry—what matters is curiosity, creativity, and the drive to turn bold ideas into reality. You’re excited not just to invent products, but to help create entirely new companies from the ground up.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The individual will ideate/research/refine novel venture hypotheses, develop the technical roadmap and business case and, and co-lead new company origination from the very early stage. A successful candidate will be a knowledgeable practitioner tuned into the latest developments in technical disciplines relevant to the life sciences, a strategic thinker with keen acumen on value creation in biotechnology driven by innovative engineering and computation, and an entrepreneur comfortable with technical and business uncertainty.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;KEY RESPONSIBILITIES&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Explore white spaces&lt;/strong&gt;: Identify and investigate emerging frontiers in AI, computation, and technology that could unlock entirely new markets and industries&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hypothesize &amp;amp; stress-test&lt;/strong&gt;: Generate bold venture hypotheses, run rapid experiments (conceptual, computational, or prototype-driven), and rigorously pressure-test assumptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design venture blueprints&lt;/strong&gt;: Help translate early-stage concepts into venture designs—including technical thesis, product architecture, and potential go-to-market approaches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Shape new companies&lt;/strong&gt;: Contribute directly to the conception and launch of high-potential ventures, with a hands-on role in their earliest stages.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaborate across disciplines&lt;/strong&gt;: Work closely with scientists, engineers, product thinkers, and entrepreneurs to fuse technical insights with market potential&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Synthesize insights&lt;/strong&gt;: Translate complex technical trends into clear, actionable insights for Flagship’s venture creation process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Push the frontier&lt;/strong&gt;: Stay ahead of emerging AI and tech advances, bringing creativity and critical thinking to areas others overlook&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;PROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE &amp;amp; QUALIFICATIONS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced degree (PhD or equivalent experience) in a technical, scientific, or quantitative field — particularly among engineering, applied physics, medical devices, chemistry, and related disciplines. We welcome diverse academic backgrounds that bring new ways of thinking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;2+ years of experience in research, technology, startups, or other environments that demand both analytical rigor and creative problem-solving&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to &lt;strong&gt;build or develop technically challenging projects&lt;/strong&gt;—whether in academia, industry, or entrepreneurial settings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort working across disciplines and rapidly learning unfamiliar technical domains&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills, including the ability to craft compelling written narra

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flagship Pioneering is a biotechnology company that invents and builds platform companies that change the world. We bring together the greatest scientific minds with entrepreneurial company builders and assemble the capital to allow them to take courageous leaps. Those big leaps in human health and sustainability exponentially accelerate scientific progress in areas ranging from cancer detection and treatment to nature-positive agriculture.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;What sets Flagship apart is our ability to advance biotechnology by uniting life science innovation, company creation, and capital investment under one roof in a way that is largely without precedent. Our scientific founders, entrepreneurial leaders, and professional capital managers are each aligned around an institutionalized process that enables us to innovate and transform for the benefit of people and planet.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Many of the companies Flagship has founded have addressed humanity’s most urgent challenges: vaccinating billions of people against COVID-19, curing intractable diseases, improving human health, preempting illness, and feeding the world by improving the resiliency and sustainability of agriculture.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Flagship has been recognized twice on FORTUNE’s “Change the World” list, an annual ranking of companies that have made a positive social and environmental impact through activities that are part of their core business strategies, and has been twice named to Fast Company’s annual list of the World’s Most Innovative Companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Associate Director, AI Operations &amp;amp; Enablement&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:60}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;The Enterprise AI team sits within Flagship&#39;s Information Technology organization and&amp;nbsp;is responsible for&amp;nbsp;AI strategy, governance, tooling, and enablement across the Flagship ecosystem.&amp;nbsp;The team works cross-functionally within IT, Legal, Finance, HR, Communications, and the firm&#39;s business and scientific functions to ensure AI is adopted safely, responsibly, and with measurable impact.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:120}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-parastyle=&quot;heading 1&quot;&gt;About the Role&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:180}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
