&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot and resolve issues related to access, performance, integrations, and usability.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as the primary subject matter expert (SME) for SharePoint across the organization.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Collaboration Platform Management&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
